article_id:3156,category_name:News,title_name:Presenting 3.5-Year Anniversary Events!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/7ec9854b6ee28e78bc28bd5a5b1a1e9d.png,message:<div>The following events for the 3.5-year anniversary start on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/7ec9854b6ee28e78bc28bd5a5b1a1e9d.png"></div><div><br></div><hr><div>1. Announcing two Gala Dragalia showcases!<br><br>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%!<br><br>The adventurer Gala Nedrick and dragon Primal Brunhilda will be featured in a Gala Dragalia starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>.<br><br>■Availability Period<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706399"></span><br><br>The adventurers Bondforged Prince and Bondforged Zethia will be featured in a Gala Dragalia starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706400"></span>.<br><br>■Availability Period<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1649224799"></span><br><br>For further information, see the respective in-game notifications or tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab for each summon showcase.<br><br>Wyrmsigils may only be redeemed in the summon showcase from which they were earned. Wyrmsigils earned from the Gala Dragalia starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> cannot be redeemed in the Gala Dragalia starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706400"></span>.<br><br></div><hr><div>2. Presenting 3.5-Year Anniversary Packs!<br><br>Anniversary packs will be available for a limited time under Value Packs in the Shop starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>.<br><br>■Availability Period<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1650002399"></span><br><br><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/2964">See here for more information.<br></a><br></div><hr><div>3. A Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon is Coming!<br><br>A Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>. During this event, log in for a chance to win items and wyrmite. If you manage to win a Scratch-A-Thon Summon, head on over to the summon screen to summon a 5★ adventurer. Don&#39;t fret if luck isn&#39;t on your side, though&mdash;if you haven&#39;t won a Scratch-A-Thon Summon by the time the final day rolls around, you&#39;ll get one guaranteed!<br><br>■Prize Lineup<br>・Scratch-A-Thon Summon<br>・Rupie &times; 1,000,000<br>・Exquisite Honey &times; 5<br>・Wyrmite &times; 50<br>・Rainbow Orb &times; 25<br>・Eldwater &times; 1,000<br>・Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 1<br><br>■Event Duration<br>・Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1649224799"></span><br><br>・Scratch-A-Thon Summon<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1650088799"></span><br><br>■Notes<br>1. The Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon prize will be available every day after 07:00 when you log in.<br>2. Dragalia Scratch-A-Thon prizes can only be accepted for a limited time.<br>3. Duplicate adventurers obtained from the Scratch-A-Thon Summon will be replaced with eldwater.<br>4. Each Scratch-A-Thon Summon session can only be performed once. Multiple sessions will stack for the duration of the event.<br><br></div><hr><div>4. Daily Free Tenfold Summon!<br><br>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcase for free once per day, starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>.<br><br>■Event Duration<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1649224799"></span><br><br><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/3155">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>5. 3.5-Year Anniversary Bonus!</div><div><br></div><div>Get the following incredible rewards when you log in during the event duration!<br><br>■Daily Rewards<br>Day 1: Wyrmite &times; 1,500<br>Day 2: Blessed Ethon Ashes &times; 35<br>Day 3: Rainbow Orb &times; 35<br>Day 4: Rupie &times; 35,000,000<br>Day 5: Omnicite &times; 1<br>Day 6: Eldwater &times; 100,000<br>Day 7: Damascus Ingot &times; 1<br>Day 8: Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 3<br>Day 9: Sunlight Stone &times; 1<br>Day 10: Wyrmite &times; 2,000<br><br>■Event Duration<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1650002399"></span><br><br>Notes:<br>1. The log-in bonus will be sent to you every day after 07:00 when you log in.<br>2. Gifts sent as log-in bonuses can only be accepted for a limited time.<br><br></div><hr><div>6. Presenting 3.5-Year Anniversary Upgrade Events!<br><br>Starting on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>, a triple drops event for Avenue to Power and a triple rupies event for Avenue to Fortune will be held alongside many other events such as triple drops for all Elemental Ruins, Dragon Trials, and Imperial Onslaught quests.<br><br><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/10085">See here for more information.<br></a><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1648360800,update_time1648357684